reviewText: Barry Manilow: Performances , Vol. 1 The Highlights was released in 1002. It is a terrific tape. My favorite songs are, It's A Miracle, Copacabana, Let's Hang On, When October Goes, and Keep Each Other Warm. Fans of Barry Manilow will like this the most.
This is a great live concert no Barry fan should be without, highly recommended.
